line_1: An' monie a fallow gat his licks,
line_2: Frae less to mair it gaed to sticks;

line_1: An' monie a fallow gat his licks,
line_2: Frae words an' aiths to clours an' nicks;

line_1: An' monie a fallow gat his licks,
line_2: An' some, to learn them for their tricks,

line_1: He, like a thorough true-bred Spaniel, licks
line_2: The hand which cuffs him, and the foot which kicks,
